definitions.definition: Characteristic of or resembling a fen ( “ characteristically alkaline wetland containing peat below the waterline ” ) ; marshy , swampy ; also, of land : containing a fen or fens.
Now chiefly of plants : growing or living in a fen.

main_definition: Characteristic of or resembling a fen ( “ characteristically alkaline wetland containing peat below the waterline ” ) ; marshy , swampy ; also, of land : containing a fen or fens.
